trans-unit.source: OrangeHRM Open Source Mobile App - How to Download the Application
trans-unit.target: OrangeHRM Open Source Mobile App - How to Download the Application

trans-unit.source: OrangeHRM Open Source mobile application allows you to apply leave, assign leave and approve leave via a mobile device. This application is available for download on both iOS and Android platforms.
trans-unit.target: OrangeHRM Open Source mobile application allows you to apply leave, assign leave and approve leave via a mobile device. This application is available for download on both iOS and Android platforms.

trans-unit.source: Download and install the application from the App Store or Play Store.
trans-unit.target: Download and install the application from the App Store or Play Store.

trans-unit.source: The following links direct you to find the app in the Play Store / App Store.
trans-unit.target: The following links direct you to find the app in the Play Store / App Store.

trans-unit.source: You may alternatively scan for the following QR code from your mobile phone camera to find and download the application.
trans-unit.target: You may alternatively scan for the following QR code from your mobile phone camera to find and download the application.

trans-unit.source: Ensure the OrangeHRM username and password credentials are entered correctly, and click LOGIN. You will be granted access to the system after successful validation of your username and password credentials.
trans-unit.target: Ensure the OrangeHRM username and password credentials are entered correctly, and click LOGIN. You will be granted access to the system after successful validation of your username and password credentials.

trans-unit.source: Once the installation is complete, open the application and follow the steps outlined below to access your OrangeHRM system.
trans-unit.target: Once the installation is complete, open the application and follow the steps outlined below to access your OrangeHRM system.
